<BaseLayout title="About" lang="en">
  <article class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      This is the personal knowledge base and project log of Nolte. Posts are drafted by
      AI from briefings, source code, and notes, and curated by a human before publishing.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every post exists in English (primary) and German. Posts that grow out of a specific
      software project link back to the corresponding repository.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
